column5: TJ is getting itchy to open. We may see the masses coming sooner than we expected. Hang on server! Can't wait to see 1,000 people come running in at once!
Thought tomorrow was a strange time to open with many leaving for BOQ...but hey TJ's the boss ! Well Monique actually but that's another story.
Nice job Rick!  I guess this is the easiest way to deal with the Proboard hassles?  Geez, I've been around for a while, this is the third board in something like 2 years??    Mike
